<p><a href="https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/20160924/lusine_sarah_m_686x320.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-34587" src="https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/20160924/lusine_sarah_m_686x320-150x150.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="150" srcset="https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/20160924/lusine_sarah_m_686x320-150x150.jpg 150w, https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/20160924/lusine_sarah_m_686x320-240x240.jpg 240w" sizes="(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px"></a>Music for &#8220;What Are You Smoking&#8221; is provided by <a href="http://lusineweb.com/releases.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Lusine</a>. &#8220;Ticking Hands&#8221; is from his album&#160;<em><a href="http://ghostly.com/releases/sensorimotor" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Sensorimotor.</a></em>&#160;&#8220;Two Dots&#8221; is from&#160;<em><a href="http://ghostly.com/releases/a-certain-distance" target="_blank" rel="noopener">A Certain Distance</a>.&#160;</em>For more about Lusine, check out <a href="http://ghostly.com/artists/lusine" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ghostly.com</a>.</p>
