INSERT INTO articles VALUES (12483, 'The 5 Best Cannabis Cookbooks for Homemade Edibles', NULL, 'cannabis-cookbooks-1280x800.jpg', '<div class="uncode_text_column"><p>Ready-made cannabis-infused <a href="https://www.leafly.com/products/edibles/snack-foods">snacks</a>, desserts, and <a href="https://www.leafly.com/products/edibles/beverages">drinks</a> are super convenient when you want a quick nibble or a light refreshment to switch up the mood. But, when you&#8217;re looking for something a bit more substantial, the kitchen is the only place that can truly satisfying a munchie void.<br>
</p>
<div id="leafly-dfp-ad-widget-mobile-medium-rectangle-809184886" class="leafly-dfp-ad-container">    </div>
<div class="leafly-inline-related-story"><a class="leafly-article" href="https://www.leafly.com/news/lifestyle/how-3-pro-cannabis-chefs-think-about-infused-cooking"><div class="leafly-thumb"><img class="" src="https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/12144249/cannabis-chefs-5-480x300.jpg"></div><div class=""><div class="leafly-article-callout-header">RELATED STORY</div><div class="leafly-article-callout-title">How 3 Pro Cannabis Chefs Think About Infused Cooking</div></div></a></div>
<p>Learning to make your own cannabis-infused dishes&#8212;from entr&#233;es to appetizers and everything in-between&#8212;doesn&#8217;t have to be a chore, yet we know navigating the countless stream of online recipes can get a little daunting. Enter the standard cookbook, an all-in-one guide chock full of recipes for easy pickings.</p>
<p>Below, discover our favorite cannabis cookbooks that will get you in gear to create some outstanding infused meals. Who knows, maybe one day you&#8217;ll become a bona-fide <a href="https://www.leafly.com/news/lifestyle/the-future-of-brick-and-mortar-marijuana-restaurants">cannabis chef</a>.</p>
<h2><em>Herb: Mastering the Art of Cooking With Cannabis</em></h2>
<figure id="attachment_58777" style="width: 840px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="size-large wp-image-58777" src="https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/23133736/herb-cookbook-1024x1024.png" alt="" width="840" height="840" srcset="https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/23133736/herb-cookbook-1024x1024.png 1024w, https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/23133736/herb-cookbook-150x150.png 150w, https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/23133736/herb-cookbook-300x300.png 300w, https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/23133736/herb-cookbook-768x768.png 768w, https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/23133736/herb-cookbook-50x50.png 50w, https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/23133736/herb-cookbook.png 1200w, https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/23133736/herb-cookbook-960x960.png 960w, https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/23133736/herb-cookbook-480x480.png 480w, https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/23133736/herb-cookbook-240x240.png 240w" sizes="(max-width: 840px) 100vw, 840px"><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">(Courtesy of Amazon)</figcaption></figure>
<p>Chefs Melissa Parks and Laurie Wolf (who was dubbed the &#8220;<a href="https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2017/04/24/the-martha-stewart-of-marijuana-edibles" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Martha Stewart of Marijuana Edibles</a>&#8221; by the New York Times) combined their culinary talents to create <em><a href="https://www.leafly.com/products/details/the-stoners-cookbook-herb-mastering-the-art-of-cooking-with-cannabis">Herb</a></em>, a gourmet, cannabis-infused cookbook for all skill levels. With stunning images shot by photographer <a href="http://www.brucewolfstudio.com/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Bruce Wolf</a>, this collection features hundreds of recipes from appetizers and entrees to drinks and desserts along with a handy guide to understanding dosage and how to make sure the potency of your <a href="https://www.leafly.com/news/lifestyle/recipe-how-to-make-basic-cannabutter">infused butter</a> or oil stays consistent.</p>
<p><strong>Shop:</strong> <a href="https://www.inkshares.com/books/herb" target="_blank" rel="noopener">inkshares.com</a></p>
<div class="leafly-inline-related-story"><a class="leafly-article" href="https://www.leafly.com/news/science-tech/dosing-homemade-cannabis-edibles-why-its-nearly-impossible-to-cal"><div class="leafly-thumb"><img class="" src="https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/11234942/dosing-homemade-cannabis-edibles-why-its-nearly-impossible-to-cal-480x300.jpg"></div><div class=""><div class="leafly-article-callout-header">RELATED STORY</div><div class="leafly-article-callout-title">Dosing Homemade Cannabis Edibles: Why It&#8217;s Nearly Impossible to Calculate Potency</div></div></a></div>
<h2><em>Cooking With Herb</em> by Cedella Marley</h2>
<figure id="attachment_58776" style="width: 840px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="size-large wp-image-58776" src="https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/23133728/cooking-with-herb-1024x1024.jpg" alt="" width="840" height="840" srcset="https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/23133728/cooking-with-herb-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/23133728/cooking-with-herb-150x150.jpg 150w, https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/23133728/cooking-with-herb-300x300.jpg 300w, https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/23133728/cooking-with-herb-768x768.jpg 768w, https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/23133728/cooking-with-herb-50x50.jpg 50w, https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/23133728/cooking-with-herb.jpg 1200w, https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/23133728/cooking-with-herb-960x960.jpg 960w, https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/23133728/cooking-with-herb-480x480.jpg 480w, https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/23133728/cooking-with-herb-240x240.jpg 240w" sizes="(max-width: 840px) 100vw, 840px"><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">(Courtesy of Penguin Random House)</figcaption></figure>
<p>The daughter of legendary singer and songwriter, <a href="https://www.leafly.com/news/lifestyle/roger-steffens-remembers-bob-marley">Bob Marley</a>, penned this compilation of recipes that fits right in with <a href="https://www.leafly.com/brands/marley-natural">Marley Natural</a>&#8217;s clean, green, holistic lifestyle brand. It gives readers the chance to try their hands at making some of her family&#8217;s favorite (mostly vegetarian) Jamaican recipes. Intimate stories of her life growing up on the island, insight into how she includes cannabis in her personal wellness routine, and directions for infused beauty treatments accompany this robust collection of recipes.</p>
<p><strong>Shop: </strong><a href="https://www.penguinrandomhouse.com/books/535264/cooking-with-herb-by-cedella-marley-with-raquel-pelzel/9780553496444" target="_blank" rel="noopener">panguinrandomhouse.com</a></p>
<p><em>Editor&#8217;s note: Marley Natural and Leafly are owned by the same company.</em></p>
<h2><em>The Vegan Cannabis Cookbook</em></h2>
<figure id="attachment_58778" style="width: 840px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="size-large wp-image-58778" src="https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/23133758/the-vegan-cannabis-cookbook-1024x1024.jpg" alt="" width="840" height="840" srcset="https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/23133758/the-vegan-cannabis-cookbook-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/23133758/the-vegan-cannabis-cookbook-150x150.jpg 150w, https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/23133758/the-vegan-cannabis-cookbook-300x300.jpg 300w, https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/23133758/the-vegan-cannabis-cookbook-768x768.jpg 768w, https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/23133758/the-vegan-cannabis-cookbook-50x50.jpg 50w, https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/23133758/the-vegan-cannabis-cookbook.jpg 1200w, https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/23133758/the-vegan-cannabis-cookbook-960x960.jpg 960w, https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/23133758/the-vegan-cannabis-cookbook-480x480.jpg 480w, https://d3atagt0rnqk7k.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/23133758/the-vegan-cannabis-cookbook-240x240.jpg 240w" sizes="(max-width: 840px) 100vw, 840px"><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">(Courtesy of Amazon)</figcaption></figure>
<p>For those who go meatless and dairy-free, this quirky cookbook lets you enjoy delicious, cannabis-infused meals and munchies without skipping a beat. Filled with cheeky illustrations and 100 simple recipes spanning all dishes, it&#8217;s designed for beginners who may be finding their way around the kitchen while looking for vegan-friendly substitutes. Note: A lot of recipes in this cookbook include soy.</p>
<p><strong>Shop: </strong><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Vegan-Cannabis-Cookbook-Delicious-Marijuana-Infused/dp/9492788101/ref=tmm_pap_swatch_0?_encoding=UTF8&amp;qid=&amp;sr=" target="_blank" rel="noopener">amazon.com</a></p>
